data.description: Townhome in walking distance to Aurora Reservoir.  Very few properties in the market area available.  Attractive modern kitchen which includes granite counters, island, and stainless steel appliances. Master bedroom with large en-suite bath and walk-in closet. Gas fireplace, full unfinished basement and a newer roof (2022).  Cherry Creek Schools. Resort style clubhouse (with fitness center), pool, and tennis courts.  Minutes from recreation, shopping, restaurants, and entertainment.  Easy commute to DTC and and DIA.  Hurry!
